Date: Fri, 8 Nov 2019 06:23:26 -0800
Subject: ice: Add ice_pf_to_dev(pf) macro
Patch-mainline: v5.5-rc1
Git-commit: 4015d11e4b9720718de7df28d25c04d08d8b6226
References: jsc#SLE-7926

We use &pf->dev->pdev all over the code. Add a simple
macro to do this for us. When multiple de-references
like this are being done add a local struct device
variable.

